{"tid":911864,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李恐難盡吸本土派票","createTime":"2018-11-22T08:44:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-23T11:07:17.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"89cb9a4d1f8f6d78bd24f13eca93bcb814a80a5f","tid":911864,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T08:44:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181122/20551948\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181122%2F20551948&d=qAGctaA1C1X%2F6UEGp%2F687DPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=0281e23c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181122%2F20551948&h=77824a9f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181122/20551948</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年11月22日 <br />\n<br />\n李恐難盡吸本土派票<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181122/large/1121cwl3005.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181122%2Flarge%2F1121cwl3005.jpg&h=116f7496&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n李卓人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】今次立法會補選中，年輕人投票意向對民主派選情有一定的影響，《蘋果》委託港大民研進行的立法會九西補選民調顯示，在18至39歲被訪者群組中，有38%人會投李卓人一票，而60歲以上群組最多人投陳凱欣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181122/large/a0203a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181122%2Flarge%2Fa0203a.gif&h=a836c71d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n長者多支持陳凱欣<br />\n<br />\n港大民調顯示，表示會投李卓人一票受訪者中，以18至39歲群組最多，有38%；而40至59歲群組有30.5%；60歲或以上只有27.1%。但其對手陳凱欣支持組合與李卓人明顯不同，其中18至39歲群組支持度只有15.6%；反而在60歲或以上被訪者群組中；有33.3%支持陳，反映陳明顯得到較多區內長者支持。<br />\n<br />\n有為李卓人助選的民主派指，他們對李獲較多18至39歲被訪者支持感意外，不過由於民調取樣中，被視為最支持激進本土年輕人是介乎18至29歲，只佔被訪者約13%，未必能全面反映年輕人投票取向，所以他認為，即使李在18至39歲中似乎得到較多支持，「但唔代表投青政游蕙禎嘅年輕人肯去投李卓人」。<br />\n<br />\n■記者梁穎妍  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n中產多投人　基層力撐欣<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n三成低學歷人士選陳<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n建制鐵票未顯露　民調只代表李有得打<br />\n陳凱欣搶部份姚松炎選民馮檢基鎅走李卓人12%票源<br />\n中產多投人　基層力撐欣<br />\n三成低學歷人士選陳<br />\n神秘男屢撕毀李卓人海報<br />\n港大民調　李卓人31% vs 陳凱欣25%23%游離票定勝負"},{"pid":"b7248977b5cb9c5f3558f56c4abad6a7e5635690","tid":911864,"uid":38666,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T08:54:56.000Z","msg":"下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/22/165316_8464babf30a446bfd028a995d4d5327f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F22%2F165316_8464babf30a446bfd028a995d4d5327f.png&h=89979046&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係支持李卓人的梁國雄話唔要本土派的票<br />\n咁未冇票囉李呃人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3e54b435a7ba0a80463965a9c5ff3d9da0de4b1","tid":911864,"uid":171192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T09:03:20.000Z","msg":"乜咁多後生投李卓人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2426dc8eed26ecdd1c5f7ef70d2e96e3e62e5c26","tid":911864,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f3e54b435a7ba0a80463965a9c5ff3d9da0de4b1","tid":911864,"uid":171192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T09:03:20.000Z","msg":"乜咁多後生投李卓人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T09:04:56.000Z","msg":"唔信"},{"pid":"9498447ec1235c4eb54ebe1b96b3873293e8b7af","tid":911864,"uid":26770,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"f3e54b435a7ba0a80463965a9c5ff3d9da0de4b1","tid":911864,"uid":171192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T09:03:20.000Z","msg":"乜咁多後生投李卓人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T10:03:24.000Z","msg":"大把黃屍係連飯民係居權案做左咩賤野